(hospitalizing,hospitalized,hospitalizes) 

1. V-T If someone is hospitalized , they are sent or admitted to a hospital. 送…住院治疗 [usu passive] 

例： Most people do not have to be hospitalized for asthma or pneumonia. 多数人不必因哮喘或肺炎住院。 

2. hospitalization N-UNCOUNT 住院治疗 

例： Occasionally hospitalization is required to combat dehydration. 治疗脱水有时需要住院。

